{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-11-trigger/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1 id=\"trigger\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#trigger\" aria-label=\"trigger permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>trigger</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>DB에서 어떤 이벤트가 발생하면 자동적으로 실행되는 프로시저</li>\n<li>여기서 이벤트는 INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE 등의 데이터 변경</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"로그-자동-저장에-활용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%97%90-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"로그 자동 저장에 활용 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>로그 자동 저장에 활용</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>유저가 닉네임을 변경하면 변경 전 닉네임의 로그를 저장하는 트리거</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"90122901508547480000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`CREATE TRIGGER log_user_nickname_trigger -- 트리거 이름\r\nBEFORE UPDATE -- 트리거 실행 시점\r\nON users FOR EACH ROW -- 트리거 기준 테이블과 실행 범위\r\nBEGIN\r\n    INSERT INTO user_nickname_logs -- 실행할 프로시저\r\n    VALUES (OLD.id, OLD.nickname, NOW()); -- OLD는 UPDATE 전의 tuple을 가리킴\r\nEND\r\n\\$\\$`, `90122901508547480000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRIGGER</span> log_user_nickname_trigger <span class=\"token comment\">-- 트리거 이름</span>\r\nBEFORE <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 트리거 실행 시점</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> users <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR EACH ROW</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 트리거 기준 테이블과 실행 범위</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">BEGIN</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">INSERT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> user_nickname_logs <span class=\"token comment\">-- 실행할 프로시저</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUES</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>OLD<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> OLD<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nickname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">NOW</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- OLD는 UPDATE 전의 tuple을 가리킴</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">END</span>\r\n$$</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"누적-테이블-업데이트에-활용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%88%84%EC%A0%81-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94-%EC%97%85%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"누적 테이블 업데이트에 활용 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>누적 테이블 업데이트에 활용</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>상품 구매마다 유저별 총 사용한 금액 누적</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"85570611236210700000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`CREATE TRIGGER sum_buy_prices_trigger\r\nAFTER INSERT\r\nON buy FOR EACH ROW\r\nBEGIN\r\n    DECLARE total INT;\r\n    DECLARE user_id INT DEFAULT NEW.user_id; -- NEW는 INSERT된 tuple을 가리킴, DECLARE로 선언과 동시에 DEFAULT 값을 할당\r\n\r\n    SELECT SUM(price) INTO total FROM buy WHERE user_id = user_id; -- INTO 키워드로 쿼리 결과를 변수에 할당\r\n    UPDATE user_total_stats SET price_sum = total WHERE user_id = user_id; -- 변수를 이용해 누적 테이블 업데이트\r\nEND\r\n\\$\\$`, `85570611236210700000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRIGGER</span> sum_buy_prices_trigger\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">AFTER</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INSERT</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> buy <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR EACH ROW</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">BEGIN</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">DECLARE</span> total <span class=\"token keyword\">INT</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">DECLARE</span> user_id <span class=\"token keyword\">INT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DEFAULT</span> NEW<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>user_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- NEW는 INSERT된 tuple을 가리킴, DECLARE로 선언과 동시에 DEFAULT 값을 할당</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token function\">SUM</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>price<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> total <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> buy <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> user_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> user_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- INTO 키워드로 쿼리 결과를 변수에 할당</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> user_total_stats <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> price_sum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> total <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> user_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> user_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 변수를 이용해 누적 테이블 업데이트</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">END</span>\r\n$$</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"여러-데이터-변경을-한번에-감지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%AC%EB%9F%AC-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EC%9D%84-%ED%95%9C%EB%B2%88%EC%97%90-%EA%B0%90%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"여러 데이터 변경을 한번에 감지 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>여러 데이터 변경을 한번에 감지</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>단 MYSQL에서는 불가능 하므로 postgreSQL를 기준으로 예시</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"72151321407811840000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`CREATE TRIGGER avg_empl_salary_trigger\r\nAFTER INSERT OR UPDATE OR DELETE -- 여러 데이터 변경을 한번에 감지\r\nON employee FOR EACH ROW\r\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION avg_empl_salary(); -- 실행할 함수\r\n\\$\\$`, `72151321407811840000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRIGGER</span> avg_empl_salary_trigger\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">AFTER</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INSERT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">OR</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> <span class=\"token operator\">OR</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DELETE</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 여러 데이터 변경을 한번에 감지</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> employee <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR EACH ROW</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">EXECUTE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FUNCTION</span> avg_empl_salary<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">-- 실행할 함수</span>\r\n$$</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>하지만 위 예시에서 해당 employee 테이블에 모든 튜플을 수정하면 트리거가 여러번 실행되는 문제가 있음</li>\n<li>예를들어 직원이 5명이 있고 이를 모두 수정하면 수정 마다 트리거 실행(<code class=\"language-text\">FOR EACH ROW</code> 때문)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"for-each-statement\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#for-each-statement\" aria-label=\"for each statement permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>FOR EACH STATEMENT</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>트리거 실행 범위를 튜플 단위가 아닌 문장 단위로 지정</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"16906753599080671000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`CREATE TRIGGER avg_empl_salary_trigger\r\nAFTER INSERT OR UPDATE OR DELETE\r\nON employee FOR EACH STATEMENT\r\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION avg_empl_salary();\r\n\\$\\$`, `16906753599080671000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRIGGER</span> avg_empl_salary_trigger\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">AFTER</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INSERT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">OR</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> <span class=\"token operator\">OR</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DELETE</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> employee <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR</span> EACH STATEMENT\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">EXECUTE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FUNCTION</span> avg_empl_salary<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n$$</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"when-조건으로-트리거-실행-제한\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#when-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%ED%8A%B8%EB%A6%AC%EA%B1%B0-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C\" aria-label=\"when 조건으로 트리거 실행 제한 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WHEN 조건으로 트리거 실행 제한</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>사용자가 기존 닉네임과 다른 닉네임으로 변경했을 때만 트리거 실행</li>\n</ul>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"33438656032200155000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`CREATE TRIGGER log_user_nickname_trigger\r\nBEFORE UPDATE\r\nON users FOR EACH ROW\r\nWHEN (NEW.nickname IS DISTINCT FROM OLD.nickname)\r\nBEGIN\r\n    INSERT INTO user_nickname_logs VALUES (OLD.id, OLD.nickname, NOW());\r\nEND\r\n\\$\\$`, `33438656032200155000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TRIGGER</span> log_user_nickname_trigger\r\nBEFORE <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> users <span class=\"token keyword\">FOR EACH ROW</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>NEW<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nickname <span class=\"token operator\">IS</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DISTINCT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> OLD<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nickname<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">BEGIN</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">INSERT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> user_nickname_logs <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUES</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>OLD<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> OLD<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nickname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">NOW</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">END</span>\r\n$$</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"trigger-주의-사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#trigger-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-